lt Video News |publisher=AVN Media Network |access-date=January 22, 2017}}</ref>\n\n== Winners and nominees ==\nThe nominees for the 34th AVN Awards were announced on November 17, 2016, at the annual AVN Awards Nominations Party at Avalon nightclub in [[Hollywood]].\n\nThe winners were announced during the awards ceremony on January 21, 2017.\n\nThe major performer awards went to [[Adriana Chechik]], [[AVN Female Performer of the Year Award]]; [[Mick Blue]], Male Performer of the Year and Hollie Hendrix, Best New Starlet. In terms of movies, the big winners were ''Suicide Squad XXX: An Axel Braun Parody'', ''The Submission of Emma Marx: Exposed'', ''The Preacher's Daughter''<ref name=\"DieScreaming\">{{cite web |url=http://www.die-screaming.com/2017-avn-award-winners-842955/ |title=Here\u2019s Who Won at the 2017 AVN Awards |author=Dan C. |date=January 22, 2017 |website=Die-Screaming |publisher=Dan C. |access-date=January 22, 2017}}</ref> and ''Natural Beauties'', each with three or more awards.\n\n=== Major awards ===\n[[File:Adriana Chechik 2016.jpg|right|thumb|150px|[[Adriana Chechik]], winner of the 2017 [[AVN Female Performer of the Year Award]]]] \n[[File:Mick Blue 2015.jpg|thumb|right|150px|[[Mick Blue]], [[AVN Award for Male Performer of the Year|Male Performer of the Year]] winner]]\n[[File:Kleio Valentien 2016.jpg|thumb|right|150px|[[Kleio Valentien]], Best Actress winner]]\n[[File:Xander Corvus 2014.jpg|thumb|right|150px|[[Xander Corvus]], [[AVN Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]] winner]]\n[[File:Greg Lansky at the 2016 AVN Awards in Las Vegas, NV.JPG|thumb|right|150px|[[Greg Lansky]], Director of the Year winner]]\n[[File:Keiran Lee 2016.jpg|thumb|right|150px|[[Keiran Lee]], Favourite Male Performer of the Year winner]]\nWinners<ref name=\"Winners\" /><ref name=\"OfficialTwitter\">{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/avnawards?lang=en |title=AVN Awards |last1=@avnawards |first1= |date=January 22, 2017 |website=Twitter |publisher=AVN Media Network |access-d