f Fame class of 2015 was announced with 27 inductees added.<ref name=2015hof>{{cite magazine|last1=Staff|first1=AVN|title=Class of 2015: Meet the AVN Hall of Fame Inductees|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/video/Class-of-2015-Meet-the-AVN-Hall-of-Fame-Inductees-583141.html|magazine=Adult Video News|accessdate=January 17, 2015}}</ref> Inductees were honored at an industry cocktail party at the AVN Adult Entertainment Expo three days prior to the awards show.\n\nThe [[List of members of the AVN Hall of Fame|AVN Hall of Fame]] inductees for 2015, \u201ca mix of high achievers who have given something to the various sectors of our industry,\u201d are as follows:<ref name=2015hof />\n* '''Founders Branch:''' [[Al Goldstein]], [[Marc Dorcel]]<ref name=2015hof />\n* '''Video Branch:''' [[Eli Cross (director)|Eli Cross]], [[Alana Evans]], Billy Glide, Porno [[Dan Leal]], [[Kaylani Lei]], Joanna Jet, [[Kelly Madison]], Andre Madness, Craven Moorehead, Wesley Pipes, [[RayVeness]], [[Will Ryder]], [[Karen Summer]], Talon, [[Tim Von Swine]]<ref name=2015hof />\n* '''Executive Branch:''' Marci Hirsch, Bonnie Kail, Howard Levine, [[Dan O'Connell (director)|Dan O\u2019Connell]]<ref name=2015hof />\n* '''Pleasure Products Branch:''' Joe Bolstad, Pavle Sedic, Ari Suss<ref name=2015hof />\n* '''Internet Branch:''' Steve Lightspeed, Lensman, Botto Brothers<ref name=2015hof />\n\n===Films with multiple nominations<!-- and awards-->===\n\n{{Col-begin}}\n{{Col-1-of-2}}\nThe following 15 films received 10 or more nominations:<ref name=\"iafd-blog-intro\">{{cite web|last1=vanzetti|title=AVN Awards Nominations 2015: Intro and Errata|url=http://blog.iafd.com/2014/11/28/avn-awards-nominations-2015-intro-and-errata/|publisher=[[Internet Adult Film Database]]|accessdate=January 17, 2015}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align: center;\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" background: #ccff00;\n|-\n! style=\"background:#89cff0\" | Nominations\n! style=\"background:#89cff0\"